 The following example shows a handler for the `SpeechRecognized` event and some of the information about the associated <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionResult>.  

```csharp  

// Handle the SpeechRecognized event.   
void SpeechRecognizedHandler(object sender, SpeechRecognizedEventArgs e)  
